Revision history for DBIO-PostgreSQL-Age

{{$NEXT}}
    - Initial release: Apache AGE graph database support for DBIO::PostgreSQL
    - DBIO::PostgreSQL::Age schema component (load_components('PostgreSQL::Age'))
    - DBIO::PostgreSQL::Age::Storage with connect_call_load_age, create_graph,
      drop_graph, and cypher()
    - Fix cypher() to inline the graph name as a SQL literal instead of
      binding it as a parameter -- Apache AGE requires the first argument
      to cypher() to be a name constant, not a placeholder
    - Add t/10-age-live.t with 16 assertions covering create_graph,
      drop_graph (cascade), cypher CREATE/MATCH with vertices and edges,
      and parameterized cypher queries against a pgvector+AGE-enabled
      PostgreSQL pod
    - Remove workspace .proverc (tests run against installed dbio core
      via dzil install)

